Package org.neo4j.graphdb

Interface ResourceIterator<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of values returned by this Iterator
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterator<T>, Resource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Result
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CloningRecordIterator, CombiningResourceIterator, EagerResult, EagerResult.EagerResultResourceIterator, Iterators.EmptyResourceIterator, MappingResourceIterator, NestingResourceIterator, NodeCursorResourceIterator, NodeLabelPropertyIterator, PrefetchingNodeResourceIterator, PrefetchingResourceIterator, ReadOnlyIndexSnapshotFileIterator, RelationshipSelections.RelationshipEntityIterator, ResourceClosingIterator, ResultSubscriber, Scanner.Scan, ShortestPath.DirectionData, WrappingResourceIterator, WritableIndexSnapshotFileIterator
    public interface ResourceIterator<T>
extends Iterator<T>, Resource
    Closeable Iterator with associated resources. The associated resources are always released when the owning transaction is committed or rolled back. The resource may also be released eagerly by explicitly calling close() or by exhausting the iterator.
    See Also:
    ResourceIterable
